{"tid":153013,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"三浦知良又破紀錄","createTime":"2017-03-12T09:08:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-12T09:09:52.000Z","uid":59700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b2025c62fe15bb390e5def25ccbf7e917674ff48","tid":153013,"uid":59700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T09:08:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fDMwuNKv6Qg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DfDMwuNKv6Qg&d=nh4ioWg9Uual2b2uu0vi%2FZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=33e90710\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fDMwuNKv6Qg</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上月底度過50歲生日的日本傳奇球星三浦知良，再度打破自己保持的日本最年長職業足球員入球紀錄，他在今日上演的乙組聯賽，為FC橫濱射入全場唯一入球，擊敗群馬草津溫泉。<br />\n<br />\n三浦知良1993年5月首度於日本職業聯賽亮相，並於同月取得首個入球。他上星期在聯賽上陣，以50歲零7日之齡，成為全球歷來上陣年紀最大的職業足球員，打破已故英格蘭球星士丹利馬菲士保持了逾半世紀的紀錄。"},{"pid":"6dd0e74e633fb1581aa795ba124477142cbca763","tid":153013,"uid":6030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T09:09:52.000Z","msg":"想買返件波衫印佢不過好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}